THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF NEVADA, REPRESENTED IN
SENATE AND ASSEMBLY, DO ENACT AS FOLLOWS:
1 Section 1. Chapter 629 of NRS is hereby amended by adding
2 thereto a new section to read as follows:
3 1. A provider of health care shall not charge a person more
4 than $30 to fill out a form for a certification required by an
5 employer pursuant to 29 U.S.C. § 2613.
6 2. The amount specified in subsection 1 must be increased or
7 decreased annually in an amount corresponding to the percentage
8 of increase or decrease in the Consumer Price Index (All Items)
9 published by the United States Department of Labor for the
10 immediately preceding year. On or before January 1 of each year,
11 the Department of Health and Human Services shall determine
12 the amount of the increase or decrease required by this subsection
13 and establish the adjusted amount to take effect on January 1 of
14 that year. The Department shall also post the adjusted amount on
15 its Internet website.
